<font color=#FFFF00>kita perlu menyepakati beberapa hal.</font>

18
00:00:58,193 --> 00:01:00,193
<font color=#FFFF00>- Apa maksudmu?
- Kita...</font>

19
00:01:01,193 --> 00:01:03,394
