579
00:35:06,745 --> 00:35:08,706
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini yang sebelumnya ditemukan Aeguk.</font>

580
00:35:08,975 --> 00:35:11,315
<font color=#FFFF00>Seo Hae Young, Nam Kang Myung,</font>

