<font color=#FFFF00>(Daehan <i>Ilbo</i>, Mei 2001, September 2007, Mei 2008)</font>

583
00:35:22,086 --> 00:35:25,196
<font color=#FFFF00>Terdapat tiga artikel di Daehan <i>Ilbo</i>...</font>

584
00:35:25,966 --> 00:35:27,196
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengenai <i>Faith Center.</i></font>

585
00:35:28,696 --> 00:35:31,396
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada satupun yang ditulis oleh Direktur Gu Tae Won
