00:35:35,665 --> 00:35:36,735
<font color=#FFFF00>(Jurnalis Kim Cheong Ki)</font>

589
00:35:37,805 --> 00:35:39,846
<font color=#FFFF00>Dibandingkan dengan aktifitas masa lalu <i>Faith Center</i>
