641
00:38:14,126 --> 00:38:15,266
<font color=#FFFF00>Dari Daehan <i>Ilbo</i>?</font>

642
00:38:15,565 --> 00:38:18,665
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kenapa para Jurnalis jadi sering sekali mendatangi
