643
00:38:18,665 --> 00:38:21,065
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya, 'kan?
Sudah 2 atau 3 kali mereka datang?</font>

644
00:38:21,906 --> 00:38:24,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Dulu sekali pernah ke sini, lalu baru-baru ini kemari lagi.</font>

645
00:38:25,536 --> 00:38:27,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini ketiga kalinya.</font>

646
00:38:27,476 --> 00:38:29,715
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf, tapi apa maksudnya itu?</font>

647
00:38:30,215 --> 00:38:33,616
