00:39:02,376 --> 00:39:03,876
<font color=#FFFF00>(Jurnalis Gu Tae Won)</font>

657
00:39:05,175 --> 00:39:06,386
<font color=#FFFF00>Insiden ini...</font>

658
00:39:07,215 --> 00:39:08,545
<font color=#FFFF00>...merupakan titik mulanya.</font>

659
00:39:08,545 --> 00:39:09,685
<font color=#FFFF00>("Penyebab Kematian Anak Penuh Luka Sekujur Tubuh Itu
Dipertanyakan")</font>

660
00:39:10,315 --> 00:39:11,915
<font color=#FFFF00>Di sini Gu Tae Won...</font>

661
00:39:12,925 --> 00:39:15,925
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan <i>Faith Center</i> mulai saling berhubungan.</font>

662
00:39:16,955 --> 00:39:18,756
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, benar. Orang ini.</font>

663
00:39:19,266 --> 00:39:22,565
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bahkan menulis tanggal dia datang ke sini.</font>

664
