<font color=#FFFF00>(Daehan <i>Ilbo</i>, Han Chul Ho)</font>

666
00:39:25,435 --> 00:39:26,536
<font color=#FFFF00>(Han Chul Ho, Splash Team)</font>

667
00:39:35,976 --> 00:39:38,376
